name: Reid Rushing
description: I am very loving and outgoing, though can also be reserved. I am independent, yet dedicated in my relationships with others. Honesty is very important to me. I value getting to know someone for who they are, and then want to grow with them. I am genuine – so what you see is what you get!! Laughing is what I do best, and try to make the most out of life. Travel is a fun part of life and I enjoy taking road trips and cruising the seas. Spending quality time with family and friends and is important to me! I’m a kid at heart and love being around children.
